<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Offener Brief des Rates</head><p>Der Rat bestätigt das rechtmäßige Eigentum des Heinrich Spörlein, Bürger zu Nürnberg, an den von Heinz von Giech bei Geiselwind beschlagnahmten 81 Schweinen.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_477" id="238r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"/>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab facs="#facs_477_r1l18">VVir ~ die <expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> des Rats
                        der Stat cʒu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> / Tun kunt
                                <expan>offenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_477_r1l19">mit diſem <expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> / daʒ für vns
                        kom cʒu ſant Gallen tag nehſt <expan>vergange<ex>n</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_477_r1l20">Heincʒ Spörlein vnſer Burger / vnd legt vns für /
                        vvie Jm Heincʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_477_r1l21">von Gich lxxxj Swein beẏ Geẏſellwinde
                                <expan>aufgehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd
                            <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> het </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_477_r1l23">vnd behub auch <del rend="strikethrough"><expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Swein </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_477_r1l22">cʒu <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> cʒeit
                                        <expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Swein </ab></add> vor vns
                        cʒu den heiligen / daʒ die ſein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_477_r1l24">vnd anderr vnſerr <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan>
                        weren Alſo / daʒ dhein auſʒman vvederteil </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_477_r1l26">noch gemaine daran <add><ab facs="#facs_477_line_1576401150237_1423">niht </ab></add> het / Mit
                                <expan>vrk<ex>unde</ex></expan> etc / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vj̃ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> viti </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_477" id="238r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab/></div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Wir, die <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> des rats der stat czu
                                <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>, tun kunt
                                <expan>offenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> mit disem
                        <expan>br<ex>ief,</ex></expan> daz für uns kom czu <app><note><q type="date">sant Gallen tag nehst
                            <expan>vergange<ex>n</ex></expan></q>16.10.1411</note></app> Heincz Spörlein, unser burger, und
                        legt uns für, wie im Heincz von Gich lxxxi swein bey Geysellwinde
                                <expan>aufgehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> het, und behub auch <add>czu
                                    <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> czeit
                                <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> swein</add> vor uns czu den
                        heiligen, daz die sein und anderr unserr <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan>
                        weren, also daz dhein auszman weder teil noch gemaine daran <add>niht</add>
                        het. Mit <expan>urk<ex>unde</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vi <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Viti.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
